{"id":3363,"date":"2024-05-05T07:53:30","date_gmt":"2024-05-05T07:53:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/?p=3363"},"modified":"2024-05-24T11:46:13","modified_gmt":"2024-05-24T11:46:13","slug":"tuyen-dung-nhan-vien-kinh-doanh-trang-tri-su-kien","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/tuyen-dung-nhan-vien-kinh-doanh-trang-tri-su-kien\/","title":{"rendered":"[Tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng] Nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean kinh doanh trang tr\u00ed s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n &#8211; sinh nh\u1eadt 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>ANGELINE \u0111ang c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u tuy\u1ec3n d\u1ee5ng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean kinh doanh s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n TRANG TR\u00cd SINH NH\u1eacT &#8211; thu nh\u1eadp up to 15 &#8211; 25 tri\u1ec7u:<\/p>\n<h2><strong>1. M\u00f4 t\u1ea3 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>T\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng<\/li>\n<li>T\u01b0 v\u1ea5n, b\u00e1o gi\u00e1, ch\u1ed1t kh\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>Theo d\u00f5i, gi\u00e1m s\u00e1t \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng, ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, thi c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng m\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5 tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n theo \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 cam k\u1ebft tho\u1ea3 thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/li>\n<li>Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn k\u1ebf to\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 thu h\u1ed3i c\u00f4ng n\u1ee3<\/li>\n<li>C\u00e1c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00e1c theo s\u1ef1 ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a tr\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u00f2ng.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3366\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-533x400.jpg 533w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-1067x800.jpg 1067w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-768x576.jpg 768w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/28cdd31f39c2cbfa2a782c962dc94e2d-600x450.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><strong>2. Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110am m\u00ea kinh doanh, ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n<\/li>\n<li>Th\u00edch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c trong m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n<\/li>\n<li>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u00e0nh th\u1ea1o MS Office, bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n c\u00e1c ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ef9 n\u0103ng giao ti\u1ebfp t\u1ed1t, linh ho\u1ea1t<\/li>\n<li>Ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p l\u1ef1c c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9, ch\u1ecbu kh\u00f3<\/li>\n<li>\u01afu ti\u00ean \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean c\u00f3 t\u01b0 duy th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9, b\u1eaft trend nhanh<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i: D\u01b0\u1edbi 30 tu\u1ed5i, \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u1eef.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>3. Quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>L\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ( l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee9ng + hoa h\u1ed3ng theo \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng) up to 8 &#8211; 25 tri\u1ec7u<\/li>\n<li>\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c training \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 c\u00e1c k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c, c\u1ea7m tay ch\u1ec9 vi\u1ec7c n\u1ebfu ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<\/li>\n<li>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u1ecdc h\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u00f9ng c\u00f4ng ty khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tham gia c\u00e1c kho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc n\u00e2ng cao chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c ( b\u00e1n h\u00e0ng, ch\u1ed1t sale, truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf\u2026)<\/li>\n<li>Thu nh\u1eadp c\u1ea1nh tranh &#8211; L\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ( l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 hoa h\u1ed3ng)<\/li>\n<li>Tham gia c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng Team building, l\u1ec5 t\u1ebft, v\u00e0 c\u00e1c ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00e1c theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>4. M\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Gen Z tr\u1ebb trung<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ebfp tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, d\u1ec5 t\u00ednh<\/li>\n<li>Kh\u00f4ng gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c chill<\/li>\n<li>N\u00d3I KH\u00d4NG V\u1edaI CH\u1eacM L\u01af\u01a0NG<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>5. \u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>20 Ng\u00f5 176 L\u00ea Tr\u1ecdng T\u1ea5n, Thanh Xu\u00e2n, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i<\/li>\n<li>Th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c: To\u00e0n th\u1eddi gian, s\u00e1ng: t\u1eeb 8h30 \u2013 12h, chi\u1ec1u: t\u1eeb 2h \u2013 6h<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><strong>6. Li\u00ean h\u1ec7:<\/strong><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Ms. Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng Nghi\u00a0 \u2013 HCNS<\/li>\n<li>Email: Nghi.angeline@gmail.com<\/li>\n<li>\u0110i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i: 0986.897.655<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-3367\" src=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9a50c81507ef46c44adf0a167b738f01.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1508\" height=\"640\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9a50c81507ef46c44adf0a167b738f01.jpg 1508w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9a50c81507ef46c44adf0a167b738f01-800x340.jpg 800w, https:\/\/angeline.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/08\/9a50c81507ef46c44adf0a167b738